  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study will examine whether serum FGF-23 and serum phosphate at baseline of kidney
      transplant recipients can predict progression of allograft dysfunction at 3 years and
      all-cause mortality at 5 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
